Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.94,0:00:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.52,0:00:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊～坑了一段時間就完全跟不上腳步了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下成累贅了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太 支援！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有件狗急的急事要向你緊急傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你語法混亂了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我試製了結社的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制服？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活動中穿著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讀作漆黑烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(686,650)}Dark Flame
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.57,0:00:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的是這件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.43,0:00:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讀作邪眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.43,0:00:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(686,650)}Evil Eye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.91,0:00:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事不疑遲明天就穿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰管你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:00:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經從中二畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是勇太的角色嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:00:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算…算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字是…剎那（F 清英）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.69,0:01:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲裡怎樣都行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 女教皇回來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日七時 B指定點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(733,650)}Rendez-vous Point B
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎…
